In the ns-allinone-2.33 folder, execute the following commands:
---------------------------------------
cp -r ns-2.33 ns-2.33-original
patch -p0 < VCD.patch
cp VCD.cc ns-2.33/apps
cp VCD.h ns-2.33/apps
cp VCDBase.h ns-2.33/apps
--------------------------------------
Then install the simulator following the instructions in the manual
